This chapter shows how to use Spring Integration 2.0 to accomplish enterprise
integration tasks. We develop a basic help desk system with the following
integrations:

Inbound:
* Java API
* HTTP form
* E-mail (IMAP)

Outbound:
* E-mail (SMTP)
* REST web service (Basecamp XML/HTTP)
* Instant messaging (XMPP)
